title: What are the numbers between 200 and 600 which are not divisible by either 4 or 6? - Quora

response.answer_text: Numbers which are not divisible by 6 or 4 ,will also be not divisible by 12. Hence, starting from 200, all the multiple of 12 between 200 and 600 will not be divisible by either 6 or 4. They are 204, 216, 228…….. 588, 600.
